課程概述 Course Description
       熟悉電子設備散熱的需求、利用傳熱原理解決散熱問題的方法，理論與實務並重Intensify student theoretical knowledge and design capability on electronic cooling problems    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    熟悉電子設備散熱的需求、利用傳熱原理解決散熱問題的方法，理論與實務並重。
 
Intensify student theoretical knowledge and design capability on electronic cooling problems.
     

